data.eml:eml: A new inquiline ant (Hymenoptera: Formicidae) in Cataglyphis and its phylogenetic relationship

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Agosti, D. (1994): A new inquiline ant (Hymenoptera: Formicidae) in Cataglyphis and its phylogenetic relationship. Journal of Natural History 28: 913-919, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.2949937
